{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"旺旺","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyzclynlAbgSxPPqHxq7MefqKHPZtVP1ff8Ct4JCvqsIKQCZeY8icBSPOicyy0MmLcNB6yzYjFEwNgN/0","content":"1.为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？<div>看书能起到立竿见影的效果，成效很难展现，正向反馈不明显。</div><div>2.为什么成效缓慢？</div><div>书本知识转化为能力需要一个过程，而且质量低的书很多，读到好书是一个概率问题。所以成效缓慢很正常。</div><div><br></div><div>解决办法:</div><div>1.改变认识，承认读书见成效是一个缓慢的过程</div><div>2.需要列一个书单，按计划读，每天不贪多，养成习惯。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7919,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492472151000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"球状闪电","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLCPB8632Nxuia6CTs7I9LbKdkG6NPFtfP9L6Fr0dibaM7qSNgmGkpnL2Ac6YEAnVmEsBzHAbu4IicjuQ/0","content":"1.为什么很难坚持看书？——因为受到的诱惑多（朋友圈、电视、游戏）<div>2.为什么会被这些诱惑——因为做这些是享受</div><div>3.为什么是享受——因为只需要被动接受、不需要主动思考</div><div>4.为什么不喜欢主动思考——把主动思考=痛苦，看书需要主动思考，于是看书=痛苦。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7914,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492469427000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"DearJoey","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyzXrk7kxiaxiarcZtoK5ibGvfiaxSOc4AUm4uYjslRRZQg8yWScKHibVDOuOqxTZic5HfXm3wFhibAvyqMy/0","content":"为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？因为现在娱乐方式很多，很吸引人。<div>为什么现在的娱乐方式很吸引人？因为这些娱乐方式很有新意，能激发人们的参与感，并且人们能从中获得放松。</div><div>为什么人们不能把看书当成放松的一种方式？因为大部分人不习惯这样做，他们习惯刷朋友圈 、看微博。</div><div>为什么不能用读书代替刷朋友圈的、看微博习惯？可以，需要针对每个人的兴趣开出书单，培养对读书的热情。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7845,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492409389000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"郭丽敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-15","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay3J1MHPAxQGN6yrKdJbWI9X6xzmUKCPn78X0urjAKAQWicAAibcgQvrz2ribr8qfnCMNsbkBMjhIw9b/0","content":"为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？<div>因为没有可看的书。</div><div>为什么没有可看的书？</div><div>附近没有书店、不知道要看什么书。</div><div>为什么不去读书小组找书单然后买来看？</div><div>感觉没什么必要，不看书也能活的好好的。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7721,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492227978000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"潇洒鳕鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UyLlHC2Q1gMdxzMwDhQicAb4RP8PgibVuS6OEZoCGk0aIWo8mMahY8wu6ic8YFFqdsInJgJAaxbe58CIgsSXQC94U/0","content":"<p>说实话，这个问题，我还真不知道能不能找出原因，但是不妨试一下吧：</p><p>W1：为什么很难坚持每天看书？——因为没有形成每天看书的习惯</p><p>W2：为什么没有形成每天看书的习惯？——因为把看书当作是一种很困难的工作</p><p>W3：为什么把看书当作一种很困难的工作？——因为意识里自动把看书从享乐这一范畴当中剔出去了</p><p>最后，想多讲一点点就是：如果直接把看书当作是生活当中正常的一种享受，一种娱乐，其实很容易就坚持下来，每天像看一集电视剧一样，把书拿出看半小时左右的时候，一天又一天，形成习惯自然而然就坚持下来了。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7710,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492180336000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Leo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSic0ds8BMCibGZ2OUAZx2wvLS7l0JfCujUnFH561QnYtbqvZs2sAcicsmYHVHeJSgYia20o2R8WfC0mn/0","content":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">用5why分析法，分析为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">W1.为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">A1.因为大多数人没时间；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">W2.为什么大多数人没时间？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">A2.因为大多数人工作很忙，时间都变成碎片</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">W3.为什么碎片时间不能看书？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">A3.因为大多数人选择在碎片时间刷朋友圈或上网；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">W4.为什么人们更倾向于选择刷朋友圈或上网？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">A4.因为朋友圈或上网可以得到即时反馈。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">W5.为什么看书不能融入即时反馈？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">A5.可以，只是需要有人设计出合适的产品</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7708,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492177891000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jenny","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQEYBMtN5kb4OpmTENFEHLicFEIfy1kicpbhTZrnQtdSqeU7tIpxhB6XZZHZ4qymOJbAxuiaaokM2GAq/0","content":"因为每天都会有其他事情占据读书时间。<div>为什么每天都有其他事情？</div><div>因为没有很好的安排时间。</div><div>为什么没有安排好时间？</div><div>因为没有计划。</div><div>为什么没有计划？</div><div>因为不知道怎么安排--》应该按照管关键度和解决度来做好时间安排</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7652,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492076797000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Frank Wan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny69mgoQxwst1pOnyjgzqvAdFLicrRtQ1EftWszvwz9E0AjlKicpvTt2ticDuiaGDvlMcUexZCPNSjNib2Cw/0","content":"为什么很难坚持看书呢？<div>因为每天各种事情充斥着生活，不看书也照样每天过的没什么异常感觉。</div><div>为什么不看书也没有什么异常的感觉呢？</div><div>因为忙忙碌碌没时间思考自己的生活也没有长远的规划和追求</div><div>为什么没追求不思考呢？</div><div>因为各种诱惑因素太多，而潜在的需求又被浮夸满足了</div><div>为什么浮夸满足了需求呢？</div><div>因为浮夸的文章更容易吸引眼球</div><div>为什么浮夸的文章更容易吸引眼球呢？</div><div>因为人都有惰性，愿意相信所谓的真言，喜欢看速效救心致富文，鸡汤安慰文，鸡血励志文</div><div>为什么这类文章传播这么好呢？</div><div>因为优质信息缺少传播者，人民的思维能力有待提升</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7639,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492064293000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张梦路","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-12","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcI0UJ2jHh6Kq7NwJg01KPhAdTxrtB27YOCDyNYflqVmOChkOmM1s8UJogTLQGWiaichDH2J1MHWWX9TCzzgwDAYgS/0","content":"<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">如何培养他们的内在驱动力和营造外在影响力？为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？</span><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">因为他们主动或被动中断读书</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">因为他们受影响？<br></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">因为他们没时间、没计划、没形成固定的习惯。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">为什么他们没时间、没计划、没形成固定的习惯？<br></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">因为他们认为读书不重要、或者本身就没有坚持的习惯很难坚持一件事。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">为什么他们认为读书不重要、没有养成坚持的习惯？<br></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">因为他们缺少内在驱动力（兴趣、利益）和外在影响力（任务驱使、生活环境）</span><br></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\"></span></p><p>如何培养他们的内在驱动力和营造外在影响力？<br></p><p>兴趣：从自己感兴趣的领域入手，从简单通俗的读物入手</p><p>利益：增加聊天的谈资</p><p>任务驱使：通过输出（可以从写吐槽写感想<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">开始，涉及书中的内容）参加线上读书会</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">生活环境：少关注些速食公众号、微博、新闻，可以从轻松娱乐又有干货内容的媒体关注开始。换个上进的环境（工作、生活、地区）。</span><br></span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">习惯养成和维护：放在每日固定日程中（如吃饭时、洗衣服时、等车时听电子书）</span></span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">不要刻意坚持而是享受或不在意（目前找不到更好的词描述）</span></span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7608,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492006953000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"柚子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-12","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZTxBjA1yfvJcK6vUiaZbqRQAicAjPVuGLUfeibCkKPCfsQSnY8PdnPfAO0ochpiccXQQWNkg8U0DK8SVvwQlZ8QQUm/0","content":"为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？<div>因为没有养成习惯？</div><div>为什么没有养成习惯呢？</div><div>因为没有按照科学的方法形成习惯？</div><div>为什么没有按照科学的方法呢？</div><div>因为太想当然认为是个简单的事情</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7594,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491992106000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"文","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEuUJBibwaegwqwa7rXILx7WPapDW7tTnawmINtpCLZRonooMm0ezL1xuuMLrs1trOmgp0gmOpYOuk/0","content":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？因为每天事情太多没有时间。为什么会没有时间？因为没有合理规划导致浪费了很多的时间，做了无用功。为什么没有合理规划？因为不知道如何去进行精力的管理且不了解关键可行矩阵。</span><br></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7502,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491877321000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay36u84xJJa5xZVbSorVQsjiaRtdKff23d2pibDW0oSbVW3r0CUiaQtIg47Itf131L8acNXmLucqib4ibt/0","content":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">1.为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？</span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">因为大多数人没有从小看书的习惯。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">2.为什么大多数人没有从小看书的习惯？</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">因为过去父母没有这个习惯，家里没有书，也没有这个氛围。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">3.为什么过去的父母没有这个习惯？</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">因为过去经济条件差，父母都忙于生活，无暇购书读书。</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">4.为什么现在的父母可以了？</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">现在经济条件好了，大家也开始有意识到看书的重要性。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7455,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491799418000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoPsccICKmhqibTHZ3c6PRPlXKQOMsQGCZVTGNkMa0625BIPiaGC4xAlvbRSOslvms4H38dWlfyorDL/0","content":"&nbsp;","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7450,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491791456000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"寒子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-09","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay51LC8HCDuYJSWhCiaGfzmy3VbcicUnvJZlFqenDgwRweEhJT3NUuHcdKOrfibQdiaxPrT2cZX8r6hsT/0","content":"问：为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？<div>答：因为看书好无聊，如果玩游戏就不难坚持了。</div><div>问：为什么会觉得看书无聊？</div><div>答：因为大部分书是专业类或提升能力、开拓思维的类别的，需要精力集中，深入思考。比起玩游戏，看书是主动学习的过程，不是享受，会比较辛苦。</div><div>问：既然能增长知识、提升能力，为什么还无法忍受辛苦？</div><div>答：因为很多时候看书（尤其是专业书）没有明确的目的，知识点零散，不成系统，也不利于以后的应用。这样就会觉得看书没什么用，枯燥又耗费精力，没有成就感，很容易放弃。</div><div>问：有时候我们抱着目的去看书，为什么也不容易坚持下去？</div><div>答：因为有目的我们会有针对性地看书，更有效。但有时为了解决某个问题，需要看大量的书，如果不设计有效的反馈机制，也容易放弃。可以考虑：经常把看过的东西应用于工作生活中；给自己一点小奖励，等等会更有效。</div>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7425,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491729807000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"施伟","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEo9P2jC2S2gtzmiaPWycP2Fd6c8Lvunc8sP0iapaIrzxCur3tMr7Bia6kYfGXE4Pn3CLxmAUW8nr6ZK/0","content":"因为他没有兴趣啊！为什么没有兴趣啊！它枯燥乏味！解决枯燥无味就能提高坚持每天看书的习惯。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7311,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491529190000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Lasia","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-06","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQPZjdCpPKAMDUgWoXUvkVcsqzWKUUicQdLPnXALcyibVu1wsfqRjk3eRcAjzJxVM32zHIhVic3cGbxd/0","content":"<p><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">1.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font>为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？</font></span></p><p><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font>因为就上班族而言，工作一天已经很累了。下班后只想休闲娱乐下，比如刷刷手机、看看剧等。</font></span></p><p><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">2.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font>为什么大家愿意花时间刷手机、看剧，而不愿意花时间学习呢？</font></span></p><p><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font>因为刷手机、看剧属于被动接受行为，不用动脑，而学习属于需要学习者参与进去的主动行为，需要动脑。</font></span></p><p><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">3.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font>为什么被动接受行为比主动参与学习的行为更易被大家接受？</font></span></p><p><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font>因为从儿童入学开始，我们接受的几乎都是老师被动传授的知识，这种方式为大家接受、习得后对此种方式习以为常。而主动参与的学习行为虽然已被广为倡导，但很多人都处于</font>“只知其名而不知其道”的地位。因此当他们看书学习，却难以看到相应收益时，就会对看书学习失去兴趣和信心，进而放弃。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7288,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491469890000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"若雨","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-06","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcI0UJ2jHh6KqxbZia6ia3HF8IalMbc2wl4E1GTVgrOv3TD6kD92XbeyKPDNH668v5v7O45WMJiaYgHSGib6hiaPocagd/0","content":"<p>1.为什么不每天看书？</p><p>因为不喜欢看书。</p><p>2.为什么不喜欢看书？</p><p>因为看书没用。</p><p>3.为什么觉得看书没用？</p><p>对自己的工作发展和个人提升没有帮助。</p><p>4. 如果看书对自己的工作<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">发展和个人提升</span>没有帮助，那你怎样实现自己的工作发展和个人提升呢？</p><p>不需要个人提升，工作发展。现在这样就蛮好的。</p><p>总结：如果这样来提问的话，我认为大多数人不坚持每天看书的主要原因是<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">认为看书对自己没有用</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">，没有看书的意愿，。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7271,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491450085000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"博学笃志","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjGcyXgjKvljRv5hsGdS0pUiaecGsLTmju6ib8JdHpQwqZqXeovGLB8HRWVxBjq0BaZpicsLFdj3dfibia/0","content":"<p>为什么很难坚持每天看书？</p><p>因为没有时间用来看书。</p><p>为什么<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">没有时间用来看书？</span></p><p>因为工作时间忙，下班后忙家务，陪孩子。有点时间，就想放松一会。</p><p>为什么图书不能让人放松？</p><p>因为虚构类的书籍容易沉浸其中，占用太多休息时间。非虚构的书籍太耗脑力而且容易有挫败感。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">为什么非虚构的书籍太耗脑力而且容易有挫败感？</span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">之前积累有限，学习新东西比较吃力，总是对自己很失望。认为自己就这样了，根本不会通过读书得到成长。<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">为半途而废的次数太多了，没有过成功的体验。不相信自己能坚持读书。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 25.6000003814697px; background-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;为什么不相信自己能坚持读书？</span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">因为遭遇挫折时总是自我怀疑和自我批评。要面对自己的挫折，学着原谅自己，以避免罪恶感让自己放弃。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7186,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491302688000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"彭兄","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XrFctaWMO6Hek8JfFDOtEWYnA1pDX3hqjFlmjKDCFj3jID1iaMsXedtNka7iaBAcWnQiaZCCzKlMFyQ/0","content":"<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">从这个题目来看，应该分析的是原计划看书的人（有兴趣或愿望或利益驱动）没有坚持下去的原因，因此应该排除掉那些本来就不爱看书的人不经常看书的情况和少部分学神学霸有良好阅读习惯的情况。</span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？</span>原因可能是：<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">遇到一些计划外的情况，影响了看书的时间，从而打断了每天看书的计划。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">why看书时间受到影响，就会中断每天看书的计划？这一天太累了，没有心情没有精力看书，不如明天再看吧。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">why太累会影响看书的心情和精力？因为看书任务压力大，造成了拖延的心理。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">why看书任务压力大？不看书就是不够进取有为，就是懒惰无能，引发了自己的焦虑。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">why看书和进取有为联系在一起？因为看书的目的性太强，太注重结果，没有享受看书的乐趣。</span></span></p>","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7113,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491148998000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Atia文晨#十点睡姑娘#","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-02","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEJq5lCFCpXV5RnEdFWCCCiaKDBWIQp8FlrjfAdWoaHcZOcmMmZj0ZqicLVVHdPBiaNG1F2lVdWvXwbXQ/0","content":"<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px !important;\">1.因为大多数人会把是时间花在太多其他事情上，没有合理分配时间</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">why？</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">因为很多人不懂得缺乏有效的时间管理知识</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">why？</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">因为学校没有教授相关知识，而且大多数人也比较缺乏时间管理意识</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7111,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491144424000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":false},"code":200}
